Description.Text: Featuring the TRENCH slim fit jeans constructed from a high quality 12 ounce 2 way stretch denim fabric. This TRENCH is a classic 5 pocket pair of jeans, skillfully finished in a dip dye effect. Additional features of this TRENCH include slitted knees, repaired patches, a genuine leather two toned branded waistband patch, antique silver branded rivet buttons and a metal coin ingot on the pocket. The heavy double stone wash creates the look and feel of authenticy.

These denims have been finished off with a beautiful bleach and heavy double stone was for autenticity.
